{"tid":2404670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院發表聲明 指出台灣是民主領頭羊 美國將致力深化美台關係","createTime":"2021-02-12T00:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T06:44:58.000Z","uid":292499,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c404f28f6d3dcea34159ad2e30ec6cae897436f8","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"由於這是美國總統拜登（Joe Biden）1月20日上任以來，蕭美琴首次進到國務院大樓，外界普遍將此視為美台關係在新政府任內也會持續正面發展的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人普萊斯（Ned Price）今天被問到此事時表示，他沒有更多關於兩人會面的細節可公布，「但廣泛來說，有鑒於台灣是民主領頭羊，也是重要經濟、安全夥伴，我們致力深化與台灣的關係」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102120009.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102120009.aspx&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=fd1175bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102120009.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"3a2c216193e5dac568e100a8ae90d62a9920ffa5","tid":2404670,"uid":297997,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"一個中國，台灣民選代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c08220bfb62f3acbb09b47f525482f672a64c64","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:31:12.000Z","msg":"普萊斯今天也駁斥部分媒體報導，拜登撤銷前總統川普任內所下達要求美國各級學校揭露與孔子學院之間協議資訊的命令。<br />\n<br />\n普萊斯表示，川普政府從未將該命令交給聯邦公報（Federal Register），因為白宮管理及預算局（Office of Management and Budget）從未完成相關審查程序，而白宮幕僚長克蘭（Ron Klain）依循前例，在拜登上任當天凍結先前所有尚未生效的規定。<br />\n<br />\n普萊斯強調，拜登政府關切中共透過孔子學院的活動，並會將孔子學院納入美國對中國利用資訊戰與其他脅迫作為，削弱並干涉民主政體之整體回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531040429baf4a504f6191b3ceb0a3492e878d6f","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a2c216193e5dac568e100a8ae90d62a9920ffa5","tid":2404670,"uid":297997,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"一個中國，台灣民選代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32d83ed96c07841e3b65e3b76821b14c49066b2","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時傾FTA"},{"pid":"ecc646acd1efb2620e3cdfa106a05c954bd96a97","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e9a07f2295042945132baeb8c85053c381c3ac","tid":2404670,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32d83ed96c07841e3b65e3b76821b14c49066b2","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時傾FTA"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T00:41:15.000Z","msg":"係。再唔傾。民進黨實比萊豬玩死"},{"pid":"21da7e6eda3188c16c3427f99112eea1e4a5288f","tid":2404670,"uid":292499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a2e9a07f2295042945132baeb8c85053c381c3ac","tid":2404670,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":